		{
			"name": "POST /config/network",
			"description": "Modifica la configuración de red persistente y **reinicia el dispositivo** automáticamente. Equivalente HTTP del comando Serial `{\"cmd\":\"set-config\",...}`.\n\n⚠️ **Alto riesgo.** Una IP estática mal configurada deja al equipo aislado por red — la única vía de recuperación es el canal Serial USB.\n\nEl reboot es diferido: el handler responde 200 primero, marca un flag, y el reset se dispara desde `loop()` una vez que la conexión TCP se cierra.\n\n**Body:**\n- `mode` (string, requerido): `\"static\"` o `\"dhcp\"`\n- `ip`, `subnet`, `gateway` (string, requeridos en modo static): formato `a.b.c.d`\n- `request_id` (string, opcional): `[A-Za-z0-9_-]{1,36}`, echo-devuelto en la respuesta\n\n**Errores 400** (no se escribe EEPROM, no hay reboot): `missing mode`, `invalid mode`, `missing ip/subnet/gateway`, `invalid ip`/`subnet`/`gateway`, `non-contiguous subnet`, `gateway not in subnet`, `invalid request_id`.\n**Error 500**: `eeprom write failed`.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Set static IP",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"mode\": \"static\",\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.1.50\",\n  \"subnet\": \"255.255.255.0\",\n  \"gateway\": \"192.168.1.1\",\n  \"request_id\": \"abc123\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": { "language": "json" }
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/config/network",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["config", "network"]
						},
						"description": "Persiste IP estática en EEPROM y reinicia. `request_id` es opcional."
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "200 OK",
							"originalRequest": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [
									{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
								],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n  \"mode\": \"static\",\n  \"ip\": \"192.168.1.50\",\n  \"subnet\": \"255.255.255.0\",\n  \"gateway\": \"192.168.1.1\",\n  \"request_id\": \"abc123\"\n}"
								},
								"url": {
									"raw": "{{base_url}}/config/network",
									"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
									"path": ["config", "network"]
								}
							},
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
							"header": [
								{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
							],
							"cookie": [],
							"body": "{\n  \"status\": \"saved\",\n  \"reboot\": true,\n  \"request_id\": \"abc123\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-24T15:30:00Z\",\n  \"time_valid\": true\n}"
						}
					]
				},
